Corporate Strategy | SusGlobal Energy Corp.





























































Leaders in Waste to Energy Management1(866) 512-7374info@susglobalenergy.com 





















aaa 























Corporate Strategy
By leveraging existing relationships in the waste to energy Industry including existing patent and both proprietary and intellectual property, SusGlobal Energy seeks to build a large and diversified portfolio of these technologies with the objective of monetizing them. The portfolio will comprise three distinct types of technologies:


1Process Source Separated Organics (“SSO”) in anerobic digestors to divert from landfills and recover biogas. This biogas can be converted to gaseous fuel for industrial processes, electricity to the grid or cleaned for compressed renewable gas.

2Debottleneck existing anerobic digestors to allow processing of SSO to increase biogas yield.

3Utilize recycled plastics to produce liquid fuels. 


